title: Have you seen it? Pending in Seattle. 2 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: This cozy cottage comes with all kinds of opportunity!
Two beds/Two baths with lots of space to expand.
Move in and personalize at your leisure or bring your vision and a plan, and take this one down to its bones in a recreation of its vintage roots!
Either way, this one is not to be missed!
Nice yard and great curb appeal in the heart of Bryant.  Shopping, coffee, dining, UW, and the Burke Gilman trail are all just minutes away!
Easy access to downtown and super easy access to anywhere in the city.
